{"tid":1715242,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警署疑遭自殺炸彈攻擊","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T05:21:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e037b8bad1bf26e85d53c50fefdc8b00d6e8e640","tid":1715242,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"印尼北蘇門答臘省（North Sumatra）警方發言人今天說，發生在首府棉蘭（Medan）警署總部外的爆炸案，疑為自殺炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，警方發言人阿特瑪加（Tatan Dirsan Atmaja）接受電話訪問時說，爆炸案發生在當地時間上午8時40分，疑為自殺炸彈客的人在攻擊中喪命，有些警察因爆炸而負傷。<br />\n<br />\n幾家印尼電視頻道拍到群眾匆忙跑出警署總部周邊建物的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201911130110.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201911130110.aspx&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=4fc5fae9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201911130110.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"03a5663efb6c9d48b7240151b5bdc6456e74686d","tid":1715242,"uid":113922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"3毛<br />\n屌你全家"},{"pid":"7acbccceaba9b6b214ac07f2789956c87f968122","tid":1715242,"uid":163797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"好撚好玩?"},{"pid":"c956e254acc1ffb7eee944514d18aa4e2c15c945","tid":1715242,"uid":332860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"4fc741dc8aa53f76cc98f12e3013a39adc60a4d6","tid":1715242,"uid":76059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"8d34963a887f781806f4dc399a1b1a89fc762678","tid":1715242,"uid":303110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"支持三毛樓主綁住炸彈去炸狗<br />\n唔做正契弟"},{"pid":"bca1a574d2f6e7fe6b71b00e66bf66100b9ec889","tid":1715242,"uid":193877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"very funny"},{"pid":"0d67b97845b1d7fb1a6a